{"tid":462244,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"原來ling u 真係好細","createTime":"2017-11-08T11:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T07:33:11.000Z","uid":156685,"like":5,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"08fc0b8e1535ea543651ccac73069194fef286e4","tid":462244,"uid":156685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"近期我聽到啲人講南宿有個人好仆街 自己拍緊拖嗰陣都要周圍溝仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽返黎就係o camp 係要報自己感情狀況 佢喺ocamp報自己感情狀況 竟然報自己係單身 嗰陣時明明係拍緊拖 咁報為左咩？梗係為左溝組仔啦 如果報自己拍緊拖 點會有仔埋身 咁佢就好似成功啦 近期俾人見到佢 周圍溝仔啦 係組仔 真係識食 有啲人問起佢上一段感情 竟然話自己上一次拍拖係兩年前 但係啲人話係近期分左冇幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁都得？<br />\n<br />\n各位lingu巴絲 知唔知係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3feddf175f3572ba041d8dfab3597a03bb7a976","tid":462244,"uid":132968,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"AREA<br />\nCUHK: 137.3 ha<br />\nHKUST: 60 ha<br />\nHKU: 53.1 ha<br />\nLingU: 9.89<br />\n<br />\nYeah I agree its quite small <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e126e3079d1ebd095cf427e6bc00c5a3b54830f1","tid":462244,"uid":11312,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"Ling u? 乜撚都細啦，圈子都細啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人識你呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d0e59e877de2f59f5ca7898fd5b17aeb1f017116","tid":462244,"uid":105890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"食過ling u ptgf 住北宿 #<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e44759cfdb659fba22576be1b8805895316f8b1","tid":462244,"uid":1767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"最細但係四年全宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm